snippet.title: Presto Starto Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on iOS, Itch.io and Google Play store!
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/presto-starto/id1520645903
Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fishmug.prestostarto
Itch.io: https://fishmug.itch.io/presto-starto

Tap! Swipe! Ready, set, go! How many times can you Presto Starto?

A fast paced reaction game from FISH MUG GAMES (Sean Rugg and Tom Cheshire)

See that button? Press it! See that toilet? Flush it! 
The long arm of ‘switching things off’ is approaching. Perform as many correct actions as you can until the lights go out!

With almost 70 randomly chosen levels, Presto Starto is the ultimate power fantasy for people who fantasise about powering things on. What are you waiting for? There’s no time to lose. Hurry up and presto subscribo for more!
